        "title": "Effortless Multi-Language Reach",
        "description": "Reach global travelers in up to 20 languages, including English, German, French, Dutch, Italian, Spanish, Portuguese, and Mandarin. Shopify's built-in tools handle translations, SEO, and localized currencies—perfect for high-end safaris and boutique lodges targeting international markets."
      },
      "addons": {
        "title": "Sell More with Add-Ons and Extras",
